Sony has officially licensed a Cloud Remote for the PlayStation 4, unveiling the device on the PlayStation Blog. The remote is programmable and uses the downloadable PDP Cloud Remote App. This allows users to access “advanced cloud technology to auto-detect devices connected to the PlayStation for hassle-free remote programming”. Sony said the benefits of the Cloud Remote include: The Cloud Remote will be available for $29.99 in the US, with pre-orders now open. It will start shipping on 18 September 2018.